name: Otoris
description:
A dark art event that captures the moment Otoris - a primary engager with the Generative force - disengages a Disruptive element from the time contained within the corridors of castle Gormenghast

It is possible this image was captured just after the subtle fracture of 'The Fabric' which provided the energy needed for the creation of 'The Thing'


PNG 7000 x 7000  ||  October 31st 2021  ||  Created by Dark Art Studio in collaboration with AI and multiple threads of a neural network and added to #HENHalloween
